(16027, '前端軟體工程師 Frontend Engineer', 'https://www.104.com.tw/job/87vdr?jobsource=joblist_search', '2024-10-11', NULL, NULL, NULL, '【工作內容】 1.負責網站前端開發 2.建立前端框架核心功能元件，並能獨力解決對開發中遇到的技術問題。 3.維護並優化頁面效能，提供使用者更好的操作體驗 4.與後端工程師協作，實現功能的設計與開發 5.依照設計文件，產出UI，及協助設計與美化。UX需與設計者，溝通討論。 【具備條件】 1.2年以上開發經驗 2.精通HTML, CSS, JavaScript及相關前端技術,能獨立從無到有產出網頁的前端開發能力。 3.對UI設計有深刻理解，能夠提供改善用戶體驗的建議。 4.熟悉javascript/Nodejs任一語言，並熟悉(react/vue)任一框架。 5.具備良好的程式除錯能力，能模組化且易維護的程式碼。 6.能在流行的瀏覽器及近期 版本正常執行前端程式的能力。 7.熟悉Restful API 並具備API串接經驗 8.具備Docker部屬經驗 9. 熟悉Git或其他版本控制系統。 【我們希望你擁有】 • 獨立解決問題的能力 • 良好的溝通能力，願意和團隊成員、主管互相討論與合作 • 能與團隊合作，確保功能需求和目標的實現 • 持續學習和研究前端技術，提升自身能力', 2),
(16028, 'Senior Backend Engineer (Roo)', 'https://www.104.com.tw/job/8829q?jobsource=joblist_search', '2024-10-11', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'We are the team mainly responsible for application development in the field of FinTech at Gogolook. Our product Roo.cash is a leading financial product matching platform in Taiwan and provides the most appropriate products that cater to each consumer’s needs in a snap. We are seeking a highly motivated Senior Backend Engineer to join our team. As a member of our team, you will have the opportunity to collaborate with colleagues to develop innovative solutions that align with future trends in the company. Welcome to join us in making an impact together! Responsibilities: 1. Design, develop, and maintain backend services for Roo team’s products. 2. Write clean and efficient code that is scalable and maintainable. 3. Document software designs and technical specifications. 4. Collaborate with cross-functional teams to ensure the outcome is delivered on time and to specifications. 5. Involvement with new product development and technology research. 6. Contribute creative and innovative idea', 2),
