(16107, 'Engineering Manager, Foundation Cloud Services', 'https://www.104.com.tw/job/898vv?jobsource=joblist_search', '2024-10-14', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PLEASE APPLY THIS JOB FROM: https://grnh.se/c8ee82581us <About the role> The Netskope Foundation Services team architects and designs services that provide reliable, scalable and high performance core functionalities for the Netskope Cloud. Which includes a configuration synchronization service propagating 100GB configurations per day across 80 data centers, and a notification aggregation service aggregating 3k events/second before sending to customers. <What’s in it for you> In this role, you will manage an engineering team and contribute to building our cloud based foundation services. Netskope has been recognized by Gartner as a market leader in the 2023 Security Service Edge (SSE) Magic Quadrant. <What you will be doing> - Managing, coaching, mentoring and encouraging the growth and career progress of team members. - Collaborating with product managers and architects to lead the design, development and delivery of key foundation services running in 80+ data centers globally. - Main', 1),
