(16109, '資料科學家 (遠端工作)', 'https://www.104.com.tw/job/8hvxi?jobsource=joblist_search', '2024-10-14', NULL, NULL, NULL, '依優先度排序： 1.依現有資料訓練模型，優化user體感。 2.依產品規則設計 AI，讓產品體驗更加真實。 3.分析資料，提出 insight、回答疑問、假設。 4.與產品開發團隊合作，開發產品的儀表板，追蹤上線成績。 5.開發 ETL 清洗資料，自己的資料自己拿。 6.維護資料品質，提供可信賴、穩定的資料。 在我們的團隊中，技能可以被培養，我們期望團隊的能力可以越來越進步，鼓勵多向發展，學習數據工程師、數據分析師的技能。 若你對數據工程師、數據分析師的職務較有興趣，請在應徵時提出，我們會視狀況做出其他安排。', 1),
(16110, 'Staff Full-Stack Engineer, UI', 'https://www.104.com.tw/job/8hwnj?jobsource=joblist_search', '2024-10-14', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PLEASE CLICK THE LINK TO APPLY: https://grnh.se/ea6ecc851us <About the role> Please note, this team is hiring across all levels and candidates are individually assessed and appropriately leveled based upon their skills and experience. The Netskope Admin Console provides our customers with a single unified view into the Netskope Platform, allowing them to fully utilize the rich set of cloud security features Netskope provides. <What’s in it for you> As a member of the UI engineering team you will collaborate with backend service teams to develop the user interface for Netskope products. You will work on both the frontend as well as the web application backend, working closely with our backend teams on Machine Learning, Threat, DLP, IaaS, API’s and other cool technologies. Depending upon the role you are hired for, you may also work on the Netskope REST API Gateway which exposes our REST API’s to customers. <What you will be doing> - Work in the frontend to implement web applications. - ', 1),
(16111, '視覺設計副理', 'https://www.104.com.tw/job/8hbff?jobsource=joblist_search', '2024-10-14', NULL, NULL, NULL, '1. 設計製作圖稿、文案、平面文宣、海報和DM等行銷助成物。 2. 規劃商品包裝的設計理念，並進行提案與執行。 3. 聯絡印刷廠進行估價、打樣之事宜。 4. 根據公司目標、商業調查、市場特性和利潤考量，規劃及執行銷售或品牌推廣策略。 5. 與零售商和批發商簽訂契約，來管理產品的配銷、建立行銷通路網絡並發展行銷通路策略。 6. 國內外展場活動規劃設計。 7. 官方網站設計及運營。 8. 其他主管交派事宜。 本工作以遠端為主，但每周將於台北或台中進行實體例會。 公司獎勵及升職機會從優，承諾視夥伴們的工作情況盡速予以拔擢，委以專項職務發展，如視覺設計經理或行銷經理等職位，歡迎有志之士加入，公司將全力支持您盡情施展抱負。', 1),
(16112, 'Sr. Software Development Engineer in Test, API Protection', 'https://www.104.com.tw/job/875el?jobsource=joblist_search', '2024-10-14', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The API Protection Team (formerly Kloudless, Inc.) is responsible for accelerating support for SaaS apps across Netskope’s CASB offering. We focus on key abstractions across the integration pipeline: Auth{n,z}, REST APIs, webhooks, and more. We use popular programming languages and cloud technologies in our stack: Go, Python, TypeScript, Angular, React, Kubernetes, Docker, Redis, ClickHouse, PostgreSQL, and more! <What this role entails> As a member of the API Protection Team you will work cross-functionally to build state-of-the-art cloud platform test automation to support our growing portfolio of API Protection solutions. <What you will be doing> - Contribute to building a flexible and scalable automation solution. - Develop and automate release engineering and security review processes. - Participate in the on-call (only during business hours) rotation to triage production issues. - Identify and communicate risks about our releases. - Own the release and be a customer advocate. - B', 1),
